          "title": "Match the Card to Your Habits",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Not all credit cards are created equal. The best card for you depends on how you spend money.",
            "15% APR, $95 annual fee, 3% groceries<br><strong>Best if:</strong> You might carry a balance occasionally",
            "18% APR, $0 annual fee, 2x travel points<br><strong>Best if:</strong> You travel and pay in full monthly",
            "22% APR, $0 annual fee, 4% gas<br><strong>Best if:</strong> Long commute, always pay in full",
            "<strong>Key Insight:</strong> If you carry a balance, APR matters most. If you pay in full monthly, rewards and benefits matter more."
